    "causal_summary": "Claude Code and OpenCode lack a structured way to delegate tasks to Google's Gemini CLI. Without a skill, agents have no guidance on when to use Gemini, how to invoke it correctly, or how to validate its output. This leads to missed opportunities for cross-AI validation, web research via Google Search grounding, and codebase investigation using Gemini's unique tools.",
